岗位职责：
1、深入集团公司半导体团队人事相关工作，制定人力资源规划并有效落地，着重高端人才员工发展、人才发掘、能力培养等方面的工作具体工作；
2、落实人员招聘、薪酬福利、绩效考核及激励政策、人员培训、团队维稳等具体工作，从而保障团队效能不断提升；
3、贯彻集团企业文化，打造沟通渠道与机制，营造健康良好劳动环境；
4、完成研究院长交办的其他工作;
任职资格：
1、本科及以上学历，7年或以上人力资源管理经验，熟练的英文或日语听说读写能力，熟悉企业管理，熟悉国家人事相关法律法规;
2、行业要求：半导体集成电路、微电子、计算机软硬件、互联网等行业经验优先;
3、较高的战略思维能力、团队领导能力、分析判断能力、团队建设及沟通协调能力、压力承受能力;

该职位涵盖人力资源六大模块，负责销售办公室全盘（薪资福利除外）人力资源日常工作。

岗位职责: 
Interview and hire applicants; prepare related documents for new comers; 
Conduct transfer / dismissal procedures and ensure they are in line with laws and regulations;
New Employee Orientation. Assit on Training structure set up, Arrange employee training, monitor the training progress and work with training vendors to arrange the training courses;
Prepare employee notices include but not limited to probation assessment notice, new comer notice, red note, contract renew and employees’transfer;
HR System maintenance; Workday system experience is preferred;
Assit Social Club actions, outing, annual party and etc. to cultivate good employee communication;
China work permit / Visa application for expats;
Other assignments assigned by HR manager.


任职资格: 
Bachelor degree in HR or related areas 
5+ years HR relevant working experience
Familiar with Office tools 
Good English communication skills
Proactive, Responsible, detail-oriented with "CAN DO" attitude
